---
const contactEmail = "honjun@tju.edu.cn";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="shell footer">
  <div class="footer-statement">
    <p>写作不是制造更多信息，<br />而是重新获得解释世界的能力。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="colophon">
    <div>
      <strong>Hong Jun</strong>
      <span>身体 · 思想 · 生计</span>
    </div>
    <nav aria-label="页脚导航">
      <a href="/subscribe/">订阅更新</a>
      <a href="/support/">支持写作</a>
      <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>写信</a>
      <a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a>
    </nav>
    <p>© {year} · 长期写作，缓慢出版</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem) 0 2rem;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--ink);
  }

  .footer-statement {
    padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
  }

  .footer-statement p {
    max-width: 15em;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.3rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .colophon {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto auto;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: end;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-dark);
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }

  .colophon div {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .colophon strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .colophon nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .colophon a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .colophon p {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .colophon {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }
</style>
